  "text": "SA ␤-Gal activity. Senescence-associated (SA) ␤-galactosidase (␤-Gal) activity was measured as previously described [CITATION_1] , except that cells were incubated in 5-bromo-4-chloro-3-indolyl-␤-D-galactopyranoside (X-Gal) at pH 5.5 to increase the sensitivity of the assay in MEFs. The percentage of cells expressing SA ␤-Gal was quantified by inspecting 200 cells per 10-cm-diameter plate three times.",
