      "span_text": "Senescence-associated (SA) ␤-galactosidase (␤-Gal) activity was measured as previously described  , except that cells were incubated in 5-bromo-4-chloro-3-indolyl-␤-D-galactopyranoside (X-Gal) at pH 5.5 to increase the sensitivity of the assay in MEFs."
